description:
This is a 63 minute workout called '60 Minute Full Body Dumbbell Workout [Strength Training]' from the channel Juice & Toya.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Tap in with us for an hour long full body strength training session! This workout is split into 4 different groups so that we can focus on targeting every muscle group. This session is not too advanced and we've included a few modifications for certain exercises. Since this workout has plenty of rest periods, we highly recommend challenging yourself with the amount of weight you're using to get the most out of this workout. Give this workout a try and let us know how you did!
